BBK01.WT5014: Exchange rates on the Frankfurt exchange /JPY 100 = DM ... / Japan

General: Spot middle rates in Deutsche Mark; difference between buying or selling rate and middle rate D-Mark 0.0015. From 1 December 1969 to 30 December 1998 official quotation on the Frankfurt exchange. From January 1999, euro reference exchange rates of the European Central Bank; see wt5630. Our specific comments refer to "Frankfurt exchange closed on ..." (Devisenbrse am ... geschlossen) or "Quotation suspended on ..." (Notierung am ... ausgesetzt).
